data.description: Welcome home to this delightful ranch-style home in Copperas Cove, Texas! This property offers modern comfort with a spacious interior, a remodeled kitchen just two years ago, two living rooms, and a generous backyard for your enjoyment. Situated on a peaceful street, it's the perfect place to call home. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!  Looking for an investment property?  This home is priced appropriately for a quick sale.
